<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Comment Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f0f2f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .comment-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 25px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .comment-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease forwards;
        }

        .comment-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .comment-author {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .comment-meta {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #777;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .comment-text {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Fade in animation */
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="comment-container">
        <div class="comment-card">
            <div class="comment-author">John Doe</div>
            <div class="comment-meta">Aug 21, 2025 | 2:30 PM</div>
            <div class="comment-text">
                This is a very informative blog post! I especially liked the section about healthy living tips.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="comment-card">
            <div class="comment-author">Jane Smith</div>
            <div class="comment-meta">Aug 21, 2025 | 3:15 PM</div>
            <div class="comment-text">
                Great article! Meditation has really helped me reduce stress and improve focus. Thanks for sharing!
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="comment-card">
            <div class="comment-author">Mike Johnson</div>
            <div class="comment-meta">Aug 20, 2025 | 10:45 AM</div>
            <div class="comment-text">
                I loved the hiking tips! I will definitely follow them on my next outdoor trip.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
